{{mp|2010 RX|30}}是由[[亚利桑那大学|亚利桑那大学]]的[[卡特林那巡天系统|卡特林那巡天系统]]在2010年9月5日发现的小型[[阿登型小行星|阿登型小行星]]<ref>{{cite news |first=Ker |last=Than |date=September 8, 2010 |title=Second Asteroid to Buzz Earth Later Today |url=http://news.nationalgeographic.com/news/2010/09/100908-asteroids-earth-nasa-catalina-sky-survey-science-space/ |work=National Geographic News |publisher=[[National_Geographic_Society|National Geographic Society]] |accessdate=2011-10-13 |archive-date=2017-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170801165935/http://news.nationalgeographic.com/news/2010/09/100908-asteroids-earth-nasa-catalina-sky-survey-science-space/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年9月8日[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]09:51，它在[[日本|日本]]上空距离地球表面248000千米的地方（月球轨道以内）掠过地球<ref>{{cite news |first=L. |last=Finch |date=September 8, 2010 |title=Harvard scientists keep an eye on wayward asteroids |url=http://www.boston.com/news/local/breaking_news/2010/09/harvard_scienti_1.html |work=[[The_Boston_Globe|The Boston Globe]] |accessdate=2011-10-13 |archive-date=2010-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100909142420/http://www.boston.com/news/local/breaking_news/2010/09/harvard_scienti_1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[NASA|NASA]]估计这颗小行星的直径约为12米，重量约为2500吨<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://neo.jpl.nasa.gov/risk/2010rx30.html |title=2010 RX30 Impact Risk |accessdate=2011-10-13 |archive-date=2010-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100912040408/http://neo.jpl.nasa.gov/risk/2010rx30.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

